OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FITV News Political Correspondent Tom
OL,7,FSheldrick gives his analysis of Donald
OL,8,FTrump's early speculation on Andy
OL,9,FBurnham's energy policy
OL,11,FAndy Burnham will pledge to restore
OL,12,Fconfidence in government and give
OL,13,Fpeople "breathing room" on the cost of
OL,14,Fliving and deliver "tangible"
OL,15,Fimprovements when he becomes prime
OL,16,Fminister on Monday.
OL,26,@uD@HOUuD@WO]vD@TOUvD@]O]
