OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784546293
OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FThe new Labour leader will set out his
OL,7,Fdomestic priorities in his first
OL,8,Fspeech from Downing Street after
OL,9,Fvisiting the Palace to "kiss hands"
OL,10,Fwith the King and formally take over
OL,11,Ffrom Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,13,FHe is expected to characterise the
OL,14,Fmoment as one of "reflection and
OL,15,Fresolution", arguing Britain must be
OL,16,Fhonest about the challenges it faces
OL,17,Fand demonstrate it can solve them.
OL,26,@qD@XOUqD@cO]vD@ROUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784546293
OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FBurnham will also say that he is
OL,7,F"acutely conscious" that the UK has
OL,8,Fhad seven prime ministers over the
OL,9,Flast 10 years, and stress the need for
OL,10,Fmore stable and responsible politics.
OL,12,FHaving come to the Labour leadership
OL,13,Fwithout a contest barely a month after
OL,14,Freturning to Westminster, Burnham is
OL,15,Fyet to set out much of his agenda for
OL,16,Fhis premiership.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784546293
OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FHe has already said he wants to
OL,7,Fdevolve power away from Westminster as
OL,8,Fone of his key priorities, driving
OL,9,Fthat agenda with a new "No 10 North"
OL,10,Fin Manchester, which he is expected to
OL,11,Fvisit later in the week.
OL,13,FPromising a "reset of priorities",
OL,14,FBurnham has also announced he will
OL,15,Fscrap Starmer's flagship digital ID
OL,16,Fprogramme in order to focus money and
OL,17,Fattention on the cost of living.
OL,26,@qD@XOUqD@dO]uD@MOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
