FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784546293
OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FIn his first week in office, the new
OL,7,Fprime minister is expected to unveil
OL,8,Fpolicies aimed at making people's
OL,9,Flives easier.
OL,11,FReports have suggested this could
OL,12,Finclude action on energy bills,
OL,13,Fincluding allowing more oil and gas
OL,14,Fdrilling in the North Sea.
OL,16,FEnvironmental campaigners have urged
OL,17,Fhim to stick to Labour's 2024
OL,18,Fmanifesto, which promised not to issue
OL,19,Fnew licences for North Sea drilling,
OL,20,Farguing they would not reduce energy
OL,21,Fbills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784546293
OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FBurnham could also face a decision on
OL,7,Fwhether to temporarily nationalise
OL,8,FThames Water as the firm struggles
OL,9,Fwith a #20 billion debt pile.
OL,11,FHe has already expressed support for
OL,12,Fgreater public control of essential
OL,13,Fservices, and Thames Water's main
OL,14,Fcreditors have said they are willing
OL,15,Fto discuss the issue with his new
OL,16,Fministers in an effort to agree a
OL,17,Frescue deal and avoid the business
OL,18,Ffalling into a so-called "special
OL,19,Fadministration regime".
OL,26,@zD@ZOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
