OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FFollowing his speech in Downing
OL,12,FStreet, Burnham is expected to begin
OL,13,Fannouncing his cabinet choices.
OL,15,FAttention has focused on who he will
OL,16,Fchoose as his chancellor, with the
OL,17,Fcontest said to be between Energy
OL,18,FSecretary Ed Miliband and Home
OL,19,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
