PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784546293
OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FAfter becoming party leader on Friday,
OL,7,FBurnham said he had still not decided
OL,8,Fon the appointment, which has been the
OL,9,Fsubject of a series of anonymous
OL,10,Fbriefings against both Miliband and
OL,11,FMahmood despite the new leader's
OL,12,Fdesire to end factionalism within
OL,13,FLabour.
OL,15,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has
OL,16,Fsuggested Burnham has no mandate to
OL,17,Frun the country, demanding a general
OL,18,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
