FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784546293
OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'acutely conscious' that
OL,4,CUK has had seven PMs over past 10 years
OL,6,FThe Reform UK leader told the CPAC GB
OL,7,Fconference in London that if he failed
OL,8,Fto enter No 10 Britain risks "turning
OL,9,Finto a third world country" within 10
OL,10,Fyears, adding that "nothing will get
OL,11,Fbetter under Andy Burnham".
OL,13,FFarage, who is fighting a by-election
OL,14,Fin Clacton after resigning as an MP in
OL,15,Fprotest at parliamentary and media
OL,16,Fscrutiny of his finances, said: "The
OL,17,Fonly certainty with Burnham is we're
OL,18,Fgoing to get more of the same, but
OL,19,Fthey'll go further to the left than
OL,20,Fthey already are."
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@[O]rD@TOUsD@ZO]xD@aOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
